INSERT INTO `XXX_papoo_language_article` SET `lan_repore_id`='2', `lang_id`='2', `header`='Item Menu Item 1', `lan_teaser`='<p><img src=\"../images/10_slide2.jpg\" alt=\"Slide 2\" title=\"Slide 2\" width=\"1200\" height=\"329\" /><br />In Papoo you have almost all degrees of freedom to create content quickly and attractively. Firmly integrated into the desired CI, you can integrate the content.</p>', `lan_teaser_link`='', `lan_teaser_img_alt`='', `lan_teaser_img_title`='', `lan_teaser_img_fertig`='', `lan_article`='<p><img src=\"../images/10_slide2.jpg\" alt=\"Slide 2\" title=\"Slide 2\" width=\"1200\" height=\"329\" /></p><p>In <a href=\"/papoo_trunk/www.papoo.de.html\" title=\"Papoo\">Papoo</a> you have almost all degrees of freedom to create content quickly and attractively. Firmly integrated into the desired CI, you can integrate the content. Degrees of freedom </p><p>The elaborate yet easy-to-use open source framework \"Foundation\" has been integrated into our CMS <a href=\"http://www.papoo.de\" title=\"Papoo\"  >Papoo</a>. This means that <span class=\"lang_en\" xml:lang=\"en\" lang=\"en\">all</span> our customers who want to design their layouts themselves with Papoo, or who frequently develop new designs, now have a comprehensive tool for grid-based and responsive website creation at their disposal.Plugins <span class=\"lang_en\" xml:lang=\"en\" lang=\"en\">Content</span> Content Content Content Content Content Content </p><p>With the help of \"Foundation\" it is possible to implement standardized and proven website structures (such as blog, two-column or three-column) in no time and fill them with content that can be integrated directly from Papoo. The subsequent adaptation or conversion of the layout is also possible without any problems. <br /> In this way, layouts can not only be created quickly, but also numerous design variants can be visualized without much programming effort, so that the best one can be retained afterwards.</p><p>Some <span class=\"lang_en\" xml:lang=\"en\" lang=\"en\">features</span> of Foundation at a glance:<br />responsive layouts, also for smartphone screens<br />own responsive image changer<br />drop-down menus<br />stylish buttons with hover effects<br />icons<br />and much more.</p><p>To get started right away, we have included a sql file in this style that contains sample content and places the various modules, such as the image changer, in the right places in the layout. <br /> ATTENTION: Importing this database overwrites all existing data. It should therefore only be imported into a new Papoo installation.</p><p>If you want to familiarize yourself with the framework, are looking for additional information or are interested in reviewing meaningful application examples, you will find what you are looking for at http://foundation.zurb.com/.</p><h3><i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-right\"></i> Total freedom</h3><p>Any number of menu items in any depth of nesting are possible. This leaves almost no wishes unfulfilled. You can place this menu at any position, top, bottom, right or left.</p><p>To each menu item you can assign one or as many articles as you like. Each menu item can have its own layout, or just its own menu item image. Of course, you can also assign any rights to each menu item, both read and write rights.</p><h3><i class=\"fa fa-lightbulb-o\"></i> Search engine optimization</h3><p>For search engine optimization we have given the versions Papoo Plus, Pro and <span class=\"lang_en\" xml:lang=\"en\" lang=\"en\">Business</span> also the possibility to give per menu item own meta and title information.</p>', `lan_article_sans`='<p><img src=\"../images/10_slide2.jpg\" alt=\"Slide 2\" title=\"Slide 2\" width=\"1200\" height=\"329\" /></p><p>In <a href=\"/papoo_trunk/www.papoo.de.html\" title=\"Papoo\">Papoo</a> you have almost all degrees of freedom to create content quickly and attractively. Firmly integrated into the desired CI, you can integrate the content. Degrees of freedom </p><p>T